{"tid":510328,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"YAMAHA MT-07馬力大　新手難操控","createTime":"2017-12-26T11:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T11:00:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dd603280933fc6b550fa32dc3523b77ee00f60da","tid":510328,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T11:00:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171226/20255553\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171226%2F20255553&d=ZmHNpoj58Zsne7T%2F4trR1AEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=0d281e7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171226%2F20255553&h=6d495eb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171226/20255553</a><br />\n<br />\nYAMAHA MT-07馬力大　新手難操控<br />\n<br />\n20,800<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171226/large/a0202a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171226%2Flarge%2Fa0202a.gif&h=390a81c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■死者早前將涉事電單車放售。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨日在九龍灣遇車禍慘死的事主鄭天佑剛甩P牌不久，有電單車車手指事主所駕駛的YAMAHA MT-07電單車，出名馬力大，速度較快，部份新手未必習慣。上周二事主才將電單車的相片上載到facebook放售，坦言：「老老實實，此車太快，未能駕馭，因此放售」，雖然他有自知之明，無奈難逃一劫。<br />\n<br />\n據運輸署資料，肇事電單車2014年首次登記，電單車油缸容量為14公升，排氣量689cc，配備四衝水冷前傾式並列雙汽缸DOHC8V引擎。香港電單車手張煒安指出，事主所駕駛的電單車YAMAHA MT-07，速度較快，對部份新手而言未必習慣。不過，該車扭力大及車身較輕，屬較易駕馭的「街車」，適合作為代步之用。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入彎太快易拋出<br />\n<br />\n亦有專家提醒鐵騎士，一般電單車司機入彎前應盡量收一收油，入完彎後，了解彎位有多深，才再慢慢加油，倘若入彎車速過快，極易被拋出墮地，並建議新手使用馬力小易操控的電單車較安全。<br />\n<br />\n■記者曾海帆  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171226/large/a0202b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171226%2Flarge%2Fa0202b.gif&h=b7858624&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n留言「此車太快未能駕馭」　放售期間出事　 剛甩P牌26歲仔　駕戰車自炒亡<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n涉詐騙500萬　凱富女董事被捕"}]}